@DataBase PhoneWizard.guide
@Node Main

 `@{b}PhoneWizard@{ub}'
 @{b}=============@{ub}

 Answerphone software for voice modems! (Version 1.7)

 This is the english documentation.

 @{" Introduction      " Link Introduction}  PhoneWizard? What is it?
 @{" Requirements      " Link Requirements}  What you need to use PhoneWizard
 @{" Configuration     " Link Configuration}  What there is to do to make it work
 @{" Tool types        " Link ToolTypes}  More ways to configure PhoneWizard
